ayelsa-1 The NCDC said that 130, 154 samples have been collected from 35 states and the Federal Capital Territory. NAN reports that the NCDC said that Its testing strategy for COVID19 is through real-time polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR). As the National Public Health Institute, it said it remains committed to supporting every state in Nigeria in response to the ongoing COVID19 outbreak. Meanwhile, the health agency said that Face shield without a face mask is not effective against  COVID-19. Vanguard Nigeria News